h2.question-author 気になること・悩んでいることを気軽に質問
h4 選択肢をつけてアンケートもできる！
- @questions.each do |question|
  .question-index-wrapper
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-8
          .question-index-single
            .user-area
              .col-xs-1.user-icon-center
                = image_tag question.user.icon_image.url,
                  src: 'Image Not Found',
                  onerror: 'this.error=null;this.src="icons/user_icon.png"',
                  class: "img-circle user-icon-center-img"
              .col-xs-10.user-question-content
                = link_to question.title, question_path(id: question.id)
                p = question.content.truncate(33)
                ul.user-margin-zero.clearfix
                  li.left = question.user.name
                  li.left = "[#{question.category}]"
                  li.left = "回答数:#{question.answers.count}"
                  li.right = l question.created_at
